lines:
1056

Quboss. 
29 So Beficia that

Ecl. 11. 1909

leane

Dear Sie

By suitake the re. 
exprea de ses sent t In Buke 
manan of ti gn, I truefne 
Enelme recipe fr 3.05

Home Reasily 
Frank In. Am bene

per b. ls, K.A.
